Reduced liquidity
Unemployment in Sinaloa during the year has been discussed by many factors, for economist Gerardo López Cervantes, director of the Faculty of Economics and Social Sciences at the Autonomous University (UAS), the rise in unemployment can be explained indirectly by actions taken in public policy.
