12 occupants left the building yesterday at noon without a fight .
It seems the nightmare of the neighbors living at 51 Balmes Street is over.
Twelve people voluntarily left the building they illegally occupied yesterday at noon, where they were holding mass parties that irritated neighbors, according to court orders without police intervention.
